WEBVTT

00:00:28.138 --> 00:00:30.964
dok shvatite da 95 procenata ideja

00:00:30.988 --> 00:00:33.615
su iste one koje ste imali juče.

00:00:33.639 --> 00:00:35.842
(Smeh)

00:00:36.647 --> 00:00:39.255
A većina mojih ideja su dosadne, u redu?

00:00:39.279 --> 00:00:40.484
Razmišljam nekako ovako:

00:00:40.508 --> 00:00:43.593
"Ah! Znam - moram pod da očistim.

00:00:43.617 --> 00:00:45.349
Ah! Zaboravila sam da prošetam psa."

00:00:45.373 --> 00:00:46.655
Moja najpopularnija misao:

00:00:46.679 --> 00:00:48.585
"Ne jedi taj kolač."

00:00:48.609 --> 00:00:50.167
(Smeh)

00:00:50.792 --> 00:00:53.928
Dakle, 95 procenata su ponavljanja.

00:00:54.567 --> 00:00:58.884
To nam ostavlja svega pet procenata
moguće šanse svakog dana

00:00:58.908 --> 00:01:01.857
da zapravo smislimo nešto novo.